(set: _doneText to "")
(if: _alreadyKnow is true)[(set: _doneText to "It is more or less what you already know. Still, it is a good reminder.")]
(else:)[(set: _doneText to "Take note of the location of the Traveler's Society on Apesai.")]
<br>


